data.description: Check out this move in ready home in the desirable Tyler's Landing Addition! As you walk inside, you will love the open floor plan between the living room, dining room and kitchen. The vaulted ceilings highlight this space as well. The kitchen has been nicely updated with subway tile backsplash, as well as, solid surface countertops. The pantry and eating bar are added bonuses, and all kitchen appliances stay! Don't miss the main floor laundry room just off the kitchen. Downstairs is the perfect spot for movie or game night. A true walkout basement is hard to find, but here it is! This home will hit everything on your checklist including an almost half acre lot, cul de sac, Maize schools, and virtually no specials! Set up your private showing today!
